tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(20),
    revenue DECIMAL,
    expenses DECIMAL,
    profit DECIMAL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ticker_symbol VARCHAR(10),
    date DATE,
    closing_price FLOAT,
    volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE financial_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(10),
    price DECIMAL,
    volume INT
);

CREATE TABLE stock_info (
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(10) PRIMARY KEY,
    company_name VARCHAR(50),
    industry VARCHAR(50),
    exchange VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE correlation_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol1 VARCHAR(10),
    stock_symbol2 VARCHAR(10),
    correlation_coefficient DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE historic_prices (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(10),
    open_price DECIMAL,
    close_price DECIMAL,
    high_price DECIMAL,
    low_price DECIMAL
);
